  "monster": {
    "title": "Witet.",
    "body": "One of the many lords of Pandemonium, Witet has an obese green body with sharp, metallic wings and a cubic structure in place of a head. Its body is covered in fungus.\n\n<lightgrey>Max HP: 195     </lightgrey><lightgrey> Will: ++++ +   </lightgrey><lightgrey>   AC: ++++     </lightgrey><lightgrey>  EV: ++        </lightgrey>                \n<lightgrey>    rF: ∞       </lightgrey><darkgrey>   rC: ...      </darkgrey><lightgrey>rPois: +        </lightgrey><lightgrey>rNeg: ∞         </lightgrey><lightgrey>rElec: ∞        </lightgrey>\n<lightgrey>Threat: Lethal  </lightgrey><lightgrey>Class: Demonic  </lightgrey><lightgrey> Size: Large    </lightgrey><lightgrey> Int: Human     </lightgrey>\nSpeed: 150% (normally travels faster than you)\n\nYou have about 81% to hit with the +5 lajatang \"Rive\" and 76% to hit with your slice and slice.\nIt has about 26% to hit you.\n\nAttack  Max Damage  \nHit     41          \n\nIt is immune to torment; and resistant to miasma.\nIt can see invisible.\nIt can fly.\nIt can open doors.\nSPELLSET_PLACEHOLDERTo read a description, press the key listed above. (AdB) indicates damage (the sum of A B-sided dice), (x%) indicates the chance to defeat your Will, and (y) indicates the spell range; shown in red if you are in range.",
